title: What's Hidden Inside This iPhone Case?
description: (   ) --- Today's Mystery Video -   TurtleCell Headphone Case for iPhone -   This iPhone accessory aims to make sure that you've always got headphones with you. It's also for those who wish that their iPhone operated more like a vacuum cleaner.  From the Amazon page -  The Turtle Cell is the first protective iPhone case with premium, built-in retractable headphones and the first solution that eliminates losing, tangling and breaking of headphones all in one device. With the Turtle Cell, simply pull the headphones out to any comfortable length and they lock into place for convenient listening. Hands-free calling is safe and easy with the in-line microphone and push button controls. When you're done using the headphones, just push a button to retract the headphones back into the case for safe storage. The case also features a built-in kickstand so you can effortlessly enjoy hands-free media anywhere. An audio switch on the bottom of the case allows users to engage or disengage the headphones without ever removing the case. The Turtle Cell is built from a high-impact polycarbonate material and has a 1mm lip over the front of the phone to provide superior protection. Even with a full-length pair of headphones and superior protection, the Turtle Cell only adds 7mm of additional thickness to your phone.
